article.description: — Jalun Trent had 27 points in Delaware's 87-80 victory against Xavier on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Trent has 27 points as Delaware takes down Xavier 87-80
article.linkText: Trent has 27 points as Delaware takes down Xavier 87-80
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Jalun Trent had 27 points in Delaware's 87-80 victory against Xavier on Tuesday night. Trent added seven rebounds and six assists for the Fightin' Blue Hens (6-3). Jyare Davis was 8 of 19 shooting (1 for 4 from 3-point range) to add 19 points. Cavan Reilly had 17 points and shot 5 for 9 (5 for 7 from 3-point range) and 2 of 3 from the free throw line. The Musketeers (4-5) were led by Quincy Olivari, who posted 34 points. Desmond Claude added 14 points for Xavier. Dayvion McKnight also put up 12 points and seven assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
